{"id": "d0fceb40-95b3-487b-86b1-b1c8ea031724", "case_id": "appeals-verify-1-airlines", "user_id": "appeals-test-user", "version": 1, "title": "Appeal Letter: My flight was cancelled and my travel insurance rejected the claim.", "content": "Dear Grievance Redressal Officer,\n\nRe: Claim Rejection for Flight Cancellation - Policy Number: [Policy Number]\n\nI am writing to express my disappointment and seek a review of the claim rejection for my flight cancellation on [Date]. As per the policy terms, I was entitled to compensation for the cancellation of my flight due to [Reason for Cancellation].\n\nHowever, the insurer has rejected my claim citing a pre-existing condition exclusion under clause 4.3. I would like to request that you review my case and provide a decision based on the policy terms and DGCA CAR Section 3 provisions.\n\nI have attached the required documents, including the physician support letter and pre-authorization form, which were missing from the initial claim submission.\n\nPlease find the details of my claim below:\n\nPolicy Number: [Policy Number]\n\nClaim Date: [Date]\n\nReason for Cancellation: [Reason for Cancellation]\n\nI would appreciate it if you could expedite the review process and provide a decision at the earliest.\n\nThank you for your time and attention to this matter.\n\nSincerely,\n\n[Your Name]\n\n", "status": "draft", "document_type": "appeal_letter", "domain": "airlines", "created_at": "2026-07-08T15:08:38.250488+00:00"}
{"id": "d94fa199-af13-45d0-8c08-3f358c38a570", "case_id": "appeals-verify-1-airlines", "user_id": "appeals-test-user", "version": 2, "title": "Complaint Email: My flight was cancelled and my travel insurance rejected the claim.", "content": "Subject: Rejected Flight Cancellation Claim - Policy Number: [Policy Number]\n\nDear Customer Care,\n\nI am writing to express my disappointment and seek assistance with my rejected flight cancellation claim. The claim was rejected due to a pre-existing condition exclusion under clause 4.3, but I believe that the policy terms and DGCA CAR Section 3 provisions support my claim.\n\nI have attached the required documents, including the physician support letter and pre-authorization form, which were missing from the initial claim submission.\n\nPlease assist me in resolving this matter and provide a decision based on the policy terms and DGCA CAR Section 3 provisions.\n\nThank you for your time and attention to this matter.\n\nSincerely,\n\n[Your Name]\n\n", "status": "draft", "document_type": "complaint_email", "domain": "airlines", "created_at": "2026-07-08T15:08:38.256851+00:00"}
{"id": "a9da8138-232f-4bca-b268-f003a2c7c4d7", "case_id": "appeals-verify-1-airlines", "user_id": "appeals-test-user", "version": 3, "title": "Escalation Note: My flight was cancelled and my travel insurance rejected the claim.", "content": "Internal Escalation Memo - Policy Number: [Policy Number]\n\nTo: Grievance Redressal Officer\n\nSubject: Rejected Flight Cancellation Claim - Policy Number: [Policy Number]\n\nThe claim for flight cancellation on [Date] has been rejected by the insurer due to a pre-existing condition exclusion under clause 4.3. However, the policy terms and DGCA CAR Section 3 provisions support the claim.\n\nThe required documents, including the physician support letter and pre-authorization form, have been submitted to the insurer.\n\nThe matter has been escalated to the IRDAI IGMS portal and subsequently to the Insurance Ombudsman.\n\nPlease note that the GRO timeline is as follows:\n\n* Initial claim submission: [Date]\n\n* Rejection of claim: [Date]\n\n* Submission of required documents: [Date]\n\n* Escalation to IRDAI IGMS portal: [Date]\n\n* Escalation to Insurance Ombudsman: [Date]\n\nPlease expedite the review process and provide a decision at the earliest.\n\nThank you for your time and attention to this matter.\n\nSincerely,\n\n[Your Name]\n\n", "status": "draft", "document_type": "escalation_note", "domain": "airlines", "created_at": "2026-07-08T15:08:38.260924+00:00"}
{"id": "cfd04ef6-fa01-438b-a2a3-724037619293", "case_id": "appeals-verify-1-airlines", "user_id": "appeals-test-user", "version": 4, "title": "Consumer Complaint: My flight was cancelled and my travel insurance rejected the claim.", "content": "Policyholder Details:\n\n* Name: [Your Name]\n\n* Address: [Your Address]\n\n* Contact Number: [Your Contact Number]\n\nPolicy Number: [Policy Number]\n\nClaim Details:\n\n* Claim Date: [Date]\n\n* Reason for Cancellation: [Reason for Cancellation]\n\n* Required Documents: Physician Support Letter, Pre-Authorization Form\n\nRejection Details:\n\n* Rejection Date: [Date]\n\n* Reason for Rejection: Pre-Existing Condition Exclusion under Clause 4.3\n\nRelief Sought:\n\n* Review of claim rejection\n\n* Compensation for flight cancellation\n\n", "status": "draft", "document_type": "consumer_complaint", "domain": "airlines", "created_at": "2026-07-08T15:08:38.269046+00:00"}
